data.description: Cute 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home on a large fenced lot.  Want a garage?  Plenty of room to build one here! Open kitchen and living area great for entertaining.  The large, enclosed back porch is nice for projects and more. Good sized room that makes a nice workshop! Nice storage shed offers room for yard tools, holiday decor and all of the other things you need space for!
